title: Caribbean Spice
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Juice bar, Take-out, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Caribbean cuisine restaurant that advertises "healthy comfort food" with a vegan section on its menu board in the restaurant. Items include such as vegan jerk chicken and vegan curry chicken, roti, veggie curry. Has tofu and uses Beyond Meat brand faux chicken, fresh juices. Cabbage and plantains are both vegan.
